mage?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fhero-china-peak.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fhero-china-peak.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fhero-china-peak.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fhero-china-peak.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fhero-china-peak.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fhero-china-peak.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fhero-china-peak.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/35\"></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto flex min-h-[620px] max-w-7xl items-center px-4 py-20 md:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl text-white\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight md:text-6xl\">Enhancing mental well being through mountain bike racing and recreation</h1><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed md:text-xl\">Join us to foster growth and resilience through outdoor experiences and competitive spirit.</p><a href=\"https://giv.li/90m43b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mt-8 inline-flex min-h-12 items-center rounded-[50px] bg-[#1a1a1a] px-8 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-black\">Donate</a></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-20 md:px-8\"><p class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#56585e]\">At Ride and Develop, we empower individuals through mountain bike racing and outdoor recreation, fostering personal growth and resilience in our community.</p><div class=\"mt-20 grid items-center gap-10 md:grid-cols-2\"><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight md:text-5xl\">Our Mission and Vision</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#56585e]\">We are dedicated to harnessing the transformative power of outdoor experiences to promote mental health, foster confident athletes through teamwork, goal-setting, and perseverance, and guide our members toward fulfilling, passion-driven careers.</p></div><div class=\"relative min-h-[320px] overflow-hidden rounded-lg md:min-h-[440px]\"><img alt=\"Rider descending a dusty trail\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fstage5.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"mt-20 grid items-center gap-10 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"relative min-h-[320px] overflow-hidden rounded-lg md:min-h-[440px]\"><img alt=\"Ride and Develop community members\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-top\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fjoe-and-mia.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#56585e]\">Ride and Develop started because we know what a bike can do—turn a tough day around, teach resilience when you crash and get back up, and connect people who might never meet otherwise. We empower stronger minds and capable riders by racing mountain bikes, giving back through trail service, sharing outdoor knowledge, and building a welcoming community where everyone belongs.</p></div></section><section class=\"bg-[#f7f7f7]\"><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-12 px-4 py-20 md:grid-cols-[360px_1fr] md:px-8\"><img alt=\"Langtown Racing Academy logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"mx-auto h-auto w-64 md:w-80\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Flta-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Flta-logo.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Flta-logo.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-semibold md:text-5xl\">Welcome to Langtown Racing Academy</h2><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#56585e]\">Discover the thrill of competitive racing with our talented team of racers at Langtown Racing Academy. Join us in our journey to excellence on course!</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-12 items-center rounded-[50px] bg-[#1a1a1a] px-8 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-black\" href=\"/support\">Join us</a><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-12 items-center rounded-[50px] border border-[#1a1a1a] px-8 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-[#1a1a1a] hover:text-white\" href=\"/racing\">The Team</a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-20 md:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-semibold md:text-5xl\">Skill Focused Learning</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#56585e]\">We provide coaching, training, and support for individuals to thrive in mountain biking and outdoor activities.</p></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2\"><article class=\"grid gap-5\"><div class=\"relative min-h-80 overflow-hidden rounded-lg\"><img alt=\"Coaching services on mountain bike trails\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fskills-cornering-coaching.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Coaching Services</h3><p class=\"leading-relaxed text-[#56585e]\">Our coaching programs empower individuals to develop skills, confidence, and resilience through mountain biking.</p><a class=\"font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] underline underline-offset-4\" href=\"/services\">View services</a></article><article class=\"grid gap-5\"><div class=\"relative min-h-80 overflow-hidden rounded-lg\"><img alt=\"Community engagement through riding\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhome%2Fkern.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Community Engagement</h3><p class=\"leading-relaxed text-[#56585e]\">Join us in fostering teamwork and personal growth through outdoor experiences and competitive racing opportunities.</p><a class=\"font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] underline underline-offset-4\" href=\"/support\">Get involved</a></article></div></section><section class=\"bg-[#f7f7f7]\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-20 md:px-8\"><h2 class=\"text-center text-3xl font-semibold md:text-5xl\">Gallery</h2><div class=\"mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-6xl grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"relative min-h-[320px] overflow-hidden rounded-lg md:min-h-[380px]\"><img alt=\"Moun